snippet.textDisplay:
Want to know an easier way to make yourself a pizza? Hmm? Okay, so Here is what ya need!

Bread.
A Toaster.
Butter.
Garlic Powder.
Spaghetti Sauce.
Cheese.
Literally any kind of meat you have.
A Microwave. Or, instead of the microwave, use a stove. Also, find yourself a nice pan.

Ready?

Okay, so, take your bread and put it in your toaster.
Butter your toast.
Garlic your toast.
Sauce your toast.
Put the meat on the toast.
Put cheese on the meat on the toast.
You can also add onion or whatever fancy stuff you want.
Heat for melted cheese.
Eat your pizza toast.
Congratulations. You made pizza! Enjoy! xD
